description: the vegan yacht is serving Austin up with delicious comfort food made entirely with ingredients that are cruelty and gmo-free. If you’re a vegan or even a meat-eater, you’re definitely going to savor every bite of this tasty, healthy cuisine that’s as good for the planet as it is for your body. The selection is simple but Mike & Danielle, the cool couple that together run this neat trailer, make all their sauces and products from scratch, all organic, like their seitan, cashew cheese, cashew sour cream, chorizos, salsas, and more. Their signature dish is the freeto burrito- organic tempeh chili and corn chips with vegan cheese n’ avocado wrapped in a flour tortilla and grilled to crispy perfection. For this and more, be sure to come on by the vegan yacht and enjoy this food that you’ll love a lot.
name: the vegan yacht
